Package: scriptvault
Type: Package
Title: Local-First Script Versioning for Reproducible Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Quentin", family = "Lably", email = "q.lamboley78@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A local-first versioning vault for research scripts and lightweight
    project assets. ScriptVault creates content-addressed archives, local branches,
    auditable history, safe restores, reproducibility records and optional RStudio
    automation without requiring Git, GitHub, or a remote service.
